sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as You (terminal)
    participant CC as Claude Code
    participant H1 as session_start.sh
    participant H2 as user_prompt_submit.sh
    participant H3 as pre_tool_use.sh
    participant H4 as session_stop_archive.sh
    participant FS as Filesystem
    participant ARC as ~/claude-archive

    U->>CC: claude (launch)
    CC->>H1: SessionStart fires
    H1->>FS: ls .claude/workbooks/
    H1-->>CC: workbook hint (≤200 tok)

    loop every prompt
      U->>CC: types a prompt
      CC->>H2: UserPromptSubmit fires
      H2->>FS: pwd, git branch, git status
      H2-->>CC: <context> block (≤30 lines)
      CC->>CC: reasons / plans / writes
      CC->>H3: PreToolUse on Bash / Edit / Write
      H3->>H3: regex check (.env, rm -rf /, curl|bash, fork-bomb)
      alt safe
        H3-->>CC: exit 0 (allow)
        CC->>FS: tool runs
      else unsafe
        H3-->>CC: exit 2 + BLOCKED message
        CC-->>U: tool blocked, ask for safer command
      end
    end

    U->>CC: Ctrl+D / /exit
    CC->>H4: Stop fires (async)
    H4->>FS: read transcript_path, cwd, session_id
    H4->>ARC: cp -n transcript + CLAUDE.md + workbooks + plans
    H4->>ARC: write MANIFEST.json
    H4->>ARC: append .archive.log line
    H4-->>CC: exit 0
